(371, 1, '2014-01-17 03:13:03', '2014-01-17 03:13:03', '<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-West-Gwillimbury-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-286 alignright" alt="Bradford West Gwillimbury Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-West-Gwillimbury-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>Bradford Ribfest 2013 is proud to present our Silver Sponsors for our 1st Annual Bradford Ribfest 2013. Their support and commitment to the event is just one of the many ways they demonstrate their commitment to the community of Bradford West Gwillimbury.\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Since 1975, the Great Gulf Group of Companies has grown from a regional home builder into one of North America’s premier real estate organizations.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Kidergy is the first and only indoor playground in Bradford and the surrounding communities. Kidergy is the ultimate indoor playground and party centre for kids.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Gold Sponsor</h3>\r\n<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Family-Dentistry-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-285 alignleft" alt="Bradford Family Dentistry Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Family-Dentistry-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>Over a century ago in 1880, David Shanahan, a young blacksmith, started building horse-drawn buggies and sleighs in Penetanguishene, Ontario. This was the beginning of the Shanahan Carriage Co. Ltd. Today, Shanahan Ford stands out as a community leader as they support the community through events like Ribfest 2013.\r\n\r\nMany thanks to Great Gulf Homes, Kidergy and Shanahan Ford for your support of this inaugural event celebrating the people of our community!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Sponsor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '224-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-17 03:13:03', '2014-01-17 03:13:03', '', 224, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=371', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(368, 1, '2014-01-15 19:06:59', '2014-01-15 19:06:59', '<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-West-Gwillimbury-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-286 alignright" alt="Bradford West Gwillimbury Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-West-Gwillimbury-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>Bradford Ribfest 2013 is proud to present our Silver Sponsors for our 1st Annual Bradford Ribfest 2013. Their support and commitment to the event is just one of the many ways they demonstrate their commitment to the community of Bradford West Gwillimbury.\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Since 1975, the Great Gulf Group of Companies has grown from a regional home builder into one of North America’s premier real estate organizations.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Kidergy is the first and only indoor playground in Bradford and the surrounding communities. Kidergy is the ultimate indoor playground and party centre for kids.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Gold Sponsor</h3>\r\n<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Family-Dentistry-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-285 alignleft" alt="Bradford Family Dentistry Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Family-Dentistry-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>Over a century ago in 1880, David Shanahan, a young blacksmith, started building horse-drawn buggies and sleighs in Penetanguishene, Ontario. This was the beginning of the Shanahan Carriage Co. Ltd. Today, Shanahan Ford stands out as a community leader as they support the community through events like Ribfest 2013.\r\n\r\nMany thanks to Great Gulf Homes, Kidergy and Shanahan Ford for your support of this inaugural event celebrating the people of our community!<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Midas-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-367 alignright" alt="Midas Logo" src="http://www.bradfordl