(886, 1, '2015-01-27 05:46:28', '2015-01-27 05:46:28', '<h3>ABOUT THE BRADFORDLICIOUS VIP PASS REWARDS CARD</h3>\r\nThe Bradfordlicious VIP Pass Rewards Card is your GOLDEN PASS to be a part of an exclusive contest giving you a 1 in 1000 chance to win our grand trip prize. You can increase your odds of winning by visiting more Bradfordlicious Restaurants. You can pick up the Bradfordlicious VIP Pass Rewards Card at the office of Summerlyn Dental Care 459 Holland St. W. Bradford. While quantities last.\r\n<h3><img class=" size-full wp-image-883 alignleft" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Blue-Mountain-Getaway.jpg" alt="Blue Mountain Getaway" width="700" height="493" /></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>ABOUT OUR CONTESTS</h3>\r\nGuests that buy any Bradfordlicious Special dinner and register your Bradfordlicious VIP Pass Rewards Card, will have additional chances to win our 2 Night Getaway to Blue Mountain Value $300.00 before taxes. Provided by Verona Travel.\r\n<h3>HOW TO WIN</h3>\r\n1. Pick up a Bradfordlicious VIP Pass Rewards Card at the office of Summerlyn Dental Care 459 Holland St. W. Bradford\r\n\r\n2. Register your Bradfordlicious VIP Pass Rewards Card with a Summerlyn Dental Care staff member.\r\n\r\n3. Visit a variety of Bradfordlicious Restaurants from more chances to win.\r\n\r\n4. Must be 19 or over to win and a legal Canadian resident.\r\n\r\n5. No purchase necessary.\r\n\r\n6.Winner will be selected on March 5th, 2015 and notified via email or phone.\r\n<h3>LIKE US &amp; FOLLOW US 2 WIN</h3>\r\nWe will be giving out A $50 Bradfordlicious Gift Card every Friday during Bradfordllcious so like our Facebook page or follow us on Twitter for your chance to win. <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Bradfordlicious/633038696742636">www.facebooks.com/bradfordlicious </a><a href="https://twitter.com/Bradfordlicious">www.twitter.com/bradfordlicious</a>\r\n\r\n<img class=" size-full wp-image-885 alignleft" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/50-Promo-Banner.png" alt="$50 Promo Banner" width="600" height="400" />\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>COMMENT 2 WIN</h3>\r\nVisit our website and tell us how your meal was at one of the restaurant pages. You could have the lucky review that wins a free meal. <a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com" target="_blank">www.bradfordlicious.com</a>\r\n<h3><img class=" size-full wp-image-884 alignleft" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Verona-Travel.jpg" alt="Verona Travel" width="700" height="493" /></h3>', 'VIP Card', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '244-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-27 05:46:28', '2015-01-27 05:46:28', '', 244, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com/244-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
