(256, 1, '2014-01-14 07:47:42', '2014-01-14 07:47:42', '<h3>Welcome to Bradfordlicious Festivals!</h3>\r\nGet ready Bradford to enjoy delicious eats from a variety of worldwide culinary offerings from over 20 restaurants this February 1<sup>st</sup> to February 28<sup>th</sup>, 2014 as the Inaugural Bradfordlicious Festival sets the stage to be a great annual event.<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/food-1261446_93935398.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-254 alignright" alt="food-1261446_93935398" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/food-1261446_93935398.jpg" width="300" height="292" /></a>\r\n\r\nRestaurant-goers will get a chance to give up their favourite restaurants to try new tastes from around the world for an unbeatable price at just $20 for a 3-course dinner and $10 for a 3-course lunch.\r\n\r\nThe 2014 Bradfordlicious event will be a fundraising endeavour in support of helping local charities, and we are looking for it to become an annual fundraiser to support local children in need. Our intention is to not only help our local charities but to make a significant difference in the community.\r\n\r\nBy inviting all residents of the Town of Bradford, and expanding our promotion and awareness to our surrounding community neighbours, we hope to help generate awareness for the charity we are supporting as well as for Bradford Businesses. By causing an increase in activity into our town, we are allowing Bradford Businesses to put themselves on display to travellers that may not have otherwise known about them.\r\n\r\n<i>Three Course Dinner Menu is to be chosen from a select menu at each restaurant. Price does not include applicable taxes, alcohol or additional menu items. Please contact the restaurants in advance for reservations. Ask about select menu.</i>\r\n\r\n<strong>General inquiries: </strong><a href="mailto:bradfordlicious@gmail.com"><strong>bradfordlicious@gmail.com</strong></a>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-14 07:47:42', '2014-01-14 07:47:42', '', 22, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=256', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
