(407, 1, '2014-01-20 00:42:10', '2014-01-20 00:42:10', 'Wimpy’s Diner is a casual dining experience adorned with the 50’s and 60’s theme with coin operated juke boxes and decorated with memorabilia the atmosphere is unbelievable and so is the food. Wimpy’s of course is known for its Famous Hamburgers, morning and all day breakfast, specialty lunches and home style dinners.', 'Wimpy''s Diner', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '62-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-20 00:42:10', '2014-01-20 00:42:10', '', 62, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=407', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(409, 1, '2014-01-20 00:51:04', '2014-01-20 00:51:04', '<img class="alignright" alt="food-1388709_83105273-420x279" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/food-1388709_83105273-420x279.jpg" width="420" height="279" />\r\n\r\nWelcome to our first annual Bradfordlicious Festival!\r\n\r\nGet ready Bradford West Gwillimbury for our first year of gourmet gastronomy with Bradfordlicious <i>2014</i>. It is the only festival in Bradford West Gwillimbury that invites you to enjoy the tastes and sounds one of your favourite restaurants ~ and try several new ones! We have worked hard to ensure you''ll have a great experience and travel the world in culinary style. Best of all, it’s far cheaper than flying... and there''s no full-body scan! With 15 restaurants participating in our first event, each with it’s own unique, delicious fixed-menu options to offer, you’ll be pleasantly satisfied!\r\n\r\n<i>Three Course Dinner Menu is to be chosen from a select menu at each restaurant. Prices do not include applicable taxes, alcohol or additional menu items. Please contact the restaurants in advance for reservations. Ask about select menu.</i>', 'Restaurants', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-20 00:51:04', '2014-01-20 00:51:04', '', 21, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=409', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(411, 1, '2014-01-20 01:43:59', '2014-01-20 01:43:59', '<h3>Title Sponsor</h3>\r\n<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-West-Gwillimbury-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-286 alignleft" alt="Bradford West Gwillimbury Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-West-Gwillimbury-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>The Town of Bradford West Gwillimbury Office of Economic Development Office is pleased to be the Title Sponsor of the 1st Annual Bradfordlicious Festival. The people in Bradford West Gwillimbury have a strong sense of community. They enthusiastically attend many public events during the year as well as a variety of events organized by community organizations.\r\n\r\nMost of these events have a business component. They generate revenue opportunities and often constitute elements of marketing plans.The 2014 Bradfordlicious event will be a fundraising endeavour in support of helping local charities, and we are looking for it to become an annual fundraiser to support local children in need.\r\n\r\nOur intention is to not only help our local charities but to make a significant difference in the community.\r\n\r\n__________________________________\r\n<h3>Gold Sponsor</h3>\r\n<a href="http://youtu.be/lB0OlFQwr_k"><img class="size-full wp-image-285 alignleft" alt="Bradford Family Dentistry Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Family-Dentistry-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>\r\n\r\nBradford Family Dentistry and Dr. Jesse Chai are very pleased to sponsor the first annual Bradfordlicious Festival.\r\n\r\nDr. Chai is the local sponsor of the Dentistry From The Heart event that was celebrated on June 7, 2013. DFTH is an international non-profit organization dedicated to providing free dental care to those who need it most. For the last 3 years, Dr. Jesse Chai and his team at Bradford Family Dentistry have donated their time and resources to host this event in downtown Bradford West Gwillimbury. This year Dr. Chai and his team were able to donate $28,800 worth of FREE DENTAL CARE to more than 100 people.\r\n\r\nFor more information, please visit his <a href="http://youtu.be/lB0OlFQwr_k">YouTube Video</a> about last years event.\r\n\r\n__________________________________\r\n<h3>Silver Sponsor</h3>\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-373 alignleft" alt="Shanahan Ford Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Shanahan-Ford-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" />\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Over a century ago in 1880, David Shanahan, a young blacksmith, started building horse-drawn buggies and sleighs in Penetanguishene, Ontario. This was the beginning of the Shanahan Carriage Co. Ltd. Today, Shanahan Ford stands out as a community leader as they support the community through events like Bradford Ribfest 2013 and now Bradfordlicious 2014</span>.\r\n\r\nShanahan knows that you have high expectations, and as a car dealer they enjoy the challenge of meeting and exceeding those standards each and every time. Allow them to demonstrate their commitment to excellence! Their experienced sales staff is eager to share its knowledge and enthusiasm with you.\r\n\r\n__________________________________\r\n<h3>Bronze Sponsor</h3>\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-377 alignleft" alt="photo copy" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/photo-copy.png" width="300" height="180" />MarlinTravel in Bradford are very pleased to sponsor Bradfordlicious 2014. <span style="line-height: 1.5em;">\r\n</span>\r\n\r\nMarlin Travel’s mission is to supply a rich platform of products that will enable our customers to enjoy a gratifying vacation purchase experience and a long term viable and trusting relationship with each of our travel advisors.\r\n\r\nMarlin Travel is a Canadian company and a proud member of Transat A.T. Inc., one of the largest vertically intergrated tourism companies in the world and Canada''s holiday travel leader. For more information, visit them today in the Walmart Plaza on Holland Street.\r\n\r\n__________________________________\r\n<h3>Media Sponsor</h3>\r\n<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Times-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-372 alignleft" alt="Bradford Times Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Times-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>The Bradford Times has been serving the <a title="Bradford West Gwillimbury" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bradford_West_Gwillimbury">Bradford West Gwillimbury</a>, south <a title="Innisfil, Ontario" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Innisfil,_Ontario">Innisfil</a> and <a title="Holland Marsh" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holland_Marsh">Holland Marsh</a> areas for over 18 years – covering local Town Council, charity and cultural events, sports and business news. It is delivered free by carrier, throughout its distribution area.\r\n\r\nBradfordlicious 2014 is proudly sponsored by the Bradford Times. Their partnership helps make this inargural event a wonderful success.', 'Sponsors', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '224-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-20 01:43:59', '2014-01-20 01:43:59', '', 224, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=411', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
