(412, 1, '2014-01-20 02:17:21', '2014-01-20 02:17:21', '<h3>Title Sponsor</h3>\r\n<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-West-Gwillimbury-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-286 alignleft" alt="Bradford West Gwillimbury Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-West-Gwillimbury-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>The Town of Bradford West Gwillimbury Office of Economic Development Office is pleased to be the Title Sponsor of the 1st Annual Bradfordlicious Festival. The people in Bradford West Gwillimbury have a strong sense of community. They enthusiastically attend many public events during the year as well as a variety of events organized by community organizations.\r\n\r\nMost of these events have a business component. They generate revenue opportunities and often constitute elements of marketing plans.The 2014 Bradfordlicious event will be a fundraising endeavour in support of helping local charities, and we are looking for it to become an annual fundraiser to support local children in need.\r\n\r\nOur intention is to not only help our local charities but to make a significant difference in the community.\r\n\r\nTo connect with us, please visit our website at: http://www.gotobwg.ca\r\n\r\n__________________________________\r\n<h3>Gold Sponsor</h3>\r\n<a href="http://youtu.be/lB0OlFQwr_k"><img class="size-full wp-image-285 alignleft" alt="Bradford Family Dentistry Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Family-Dentistry-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>\r\n\r\nBradford Family Dentistry and Dr. Jesse Chai are very pleased to sponsor the first annual Bradfordlicious Festival.\r\n\r\nDr. Chai is the local sponsor of the Dentistry From The Heart event that was celebrated on June 7, 2013. DFTH is an international non-profit organization dedicated to providing free dental care to those who need it most. For the last 3 years, Dr. Jesse Chai