member of Transat A.T. Inc., one of the largest vertically intergrated tourism companies in the world and Canada''s holiday travel leader. For more information, visit them today in the Walmart Plaza on Holland Street.\r\n\r\n__________________________________\r\n<h3>Media Sponsor</h3>\r\n<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Times-Logo.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-372 alignleft" alt="Bradford Times Logo" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Bradford-Times-Logo.png" width="300" height="180" /></a>The Bradford Times has been serving the <a title="Bradford West Gwillimbury" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bradford_West_Gwillimbury">Bradford West Gwillimbury</a>, south <a title="Innisfil, Ontario" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Innisfil,_Ontario">Innisfil</a> and <a title="Holland Marsh" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holland_Marsh">Holland Marsh</a> areas for over 18 years – covering local Town Council, charity and cultural events, sports and business news. It is delivered free by carrier, throughout its distribution area.\r\n\r\nBradfordlicious 2014 is proudly sponsored by the Bradford Times. Their partnership helps make this inargural event a wonderful success.', 'Sponsors', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '224-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-20 02:17:21', '2014-01-20 02:17:21', '', 224, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=412', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
