(503, 1, '2014-01-22 08:52:34', '2014-01-22 08:52:34', '[details address="136 Holland St E #1, Bradford, ON L3Z 2B7" latitude="44.11533" longitude="-79.56013"  phone="(905)551-1600 " hours="Sun, Mon, Wed 11am - 8pm\r\n\r\nThurs - Sat 11am - 9pm,  Tues - Closed"]\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Bangkok Saigon Noodle, offering a fusion of Thai and Vietnamese food. Owners Heuang Souvannalath and Kevin Theng have come up with a menu that provides a range of taste experiences - from crispy spring rolls, to Satays and Pad Thai noodle dishes, and from mild to hot. Specialties include "Drunken Noodles", cooked in white wine, and a Mango salad that is both refreshing, and has bite!</span>\r\n\r\nAll dishes are freshly made in Bangkok Saigon Noodle''s kitchens, with great attention to detail, and to the customer''s spicy preferences.\r\n<table width="127" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><colgroup> <col width="127" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="xl65" style="height: 19.95pt; width: 95pt;" width="127" height="26"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">(905) 775-1688</span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Bangkok Saigon', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '386-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 08:52:34', '2014-01-22 08:52:34', '', 386, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=503', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(504, 1, '2014-01-22 08:55:15', '2014-01-22 08:55:15', '[details address="1812 County 27, Bradford West Gwillimbury, ON L0G 1T0" latitude="44.04009" longitude="-79.66371" phone="(905)-939-7777" website="www.1812grillhouse.com"\r\nhours="Mon &amp; Tues closed\r\n\r\nWed 4pm - 10pm\r\n\r\nThurs &amp; Fri 4pm - 1am\r\n\r\nSat 12pm - 1am\r\n\r\nSun 2pm - 8pm"]\r\n\r\nLet a team with over 25 years of combined experience in the hospitality industry provide you top-shelf service in what we love to do!\r\nA group of dynamic hospitality industry leaders came together in 2012 to create 1812 GrillHouse. The demand for innovative event solutions outside of the GTA as well as the desire for successful events in the social and private sectors became the focus of our company. As a client of 1812 GrillHouse, you will be immersed in the top talent this town has to offer that will create a memorable experience with unparalleled service. A completely seamless execution will provide you with a professional event filled with sophistication, flare and uniqueness.\r\n<h1>BRADFORDLICIOUS SPECIAL</h1>\r\n<h2>Appetizers (pick one)</h2>\r\n1812 Organic Greens with Roasted Pecan Balsamic dressing\r\n\r\nSouthern Chicken &amp; Shrimp Gumbo\r\n\r\nJalapeno Corn &amp; Cheddar Muffins with Apple Butter\r\n<h2>Entrees (pick one)</h2>\r\nSouthern Fried Chicken &amp; Waffles\r\n\r\nJambalaya Louisiana\r\n\r\nChicken Fried Steak\r\n<h2>Dessert</h2>\r\nPeanut Butter Mud Pie &amp; Ice Cream\r\n\r\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nDrinks, Taxes &amp; Gratuity are extra. Excludes Valentines Day and Family Day. Call ahead for reservations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '1812 Grillhouse', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '157-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 08:55:15', '2014-01-22 08:55:15', '', 157, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=504', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(505, 1, '2014-01-22 08:55:59', '2014-01-22 08:55:59', '[details address="32 Holland St E, Bradford West Gwillimbury, ON L3Z 2B4" latitude="44.11445" longitude="-79.56371" phone="(905)778-8118" hours="Mon &amp; Tues closed\r\n\r\nWed 4pm - 10pm\r\n\r\nThurs &amp; Fri 4pm - 1am\r\n\r\nSat 12pm - 1am\r\n\r\nSun 12pm - 8pm" website="www.bigmommas.goldbook.ca"]\r\n\r\nIt’s Jamaica without the Beach. <span style="line-height: 1.5em;">This restaurant is an absolute jewel in the middle of downtown Bradford West Gwillimbury.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5em;">A warm welcome from the owner and authentic Jamaican menu. The food is </span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">wonderful with generous portions and lots of specials to choose from, including </span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Jamaican drinks. The food is served in a great ambiance with Reggae being played </span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">in the background.</span>\r\n\r\nAlthough not obvious from the main road, the restaurant is <span style="line-height: 1.5em;">frequented by plenty of locals who flock to the place. The menu is priced very </span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">reasonably. A must if you are in the area or just passing through.</span>', 'Big Momma''s', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '153-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 08:55:59', '2014-01-22 08:55:59', '', 153, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=505', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(506, 1, '2014-01-22 08:57:58', '2014-01-22 08:57:58', '[details address="1 Holland St W Bradford, ON L3Z 1A9" latitude="44.11568" longitude="-79.55915" phone="(905)775-8898" website="www.coffeeculturecafe.com" hours="Mon to Thurs 6am - 11pm\r\n\r\nFri to Sun 6am - Midnight"]\r\n\r\nBe part of our Culture Some appreciate the rich colors and comfortable seating, others enjoyed the delicious coffees, specialities and tasty treats. North America is filled with coffee options. North America is world famous for “grab and go” coffee. So what is causing the explosion of coffee excitement? Coffee Culture Café &amp; Eatery has chosen the theme “Come for the Taste, Stay for a Visit!”\r\n\r\nAnyone who has traveled will recognize that Coffee Culture is designed as an Old World style coffee house where customers make it a frequent destination for conversation and relaxation.', 'Coffee Culture', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '151-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 08:57:58', '2014-01-22 08:57:58', '', 151, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=506', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(507, 1, '2014-01-22 08:58:25', '2014-01-22 08:58:25', '[details address="15 Holland St E Bradford, ON L3Z 2B3" latitude="44.11451" longitude="-79.56427" phone="(905)775-6763" website="www.dutchtreats.ca" hours="Sun &amp; Mon Closed\r\n\r\nTues to Sat 9am - 5:30pm"]\r\n\r\nDutch Treats &amp; Oma''s Kitchen Cafe invites you to visit our store and stay for a "Light Tea" or an "Afternoon Tea" in our Cafe/Tea Room! A truly unique experience from deli &amp; grilled sandwiches, to croquettes, quiche and Poffertjes (mini puff pancakes served with whipping cream)!\r\n\r\nBrowse our store &amp; gift shop and sample our imported cheeses. A European deli, along with gourmet chocolates, our new gift shop filled with unique collectibles, for Hostess gifts, housewarming gifts, to our custom designed Gift Baskets!', 'Dutch Treats', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '144-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 08:58:25', '2014-01-22 08:58:25', '', 144, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=507', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(508, 1, '2014-01-22 08:59:21', '2014-01-22 08:59:21', '[details address="32 Holland St E Bradford, ON L3Z 2B4" latitude="44.11445" longitude="-79.56371" phone="(905)775-5581" website="www.lamexicanada.com" hours="Mon Closed\r\n\r\nTues 4pm - 10pm\r\n\r\nWed to Sat 12pm - 11pm"]\r\n\r\nLa Mexicanada owner Noe Martinez, in Bradford Ontario made his reputation serving authentic home-made Mexico City food to Mexican migrant workers in the Holland Marsh. He keeps sombreros on hand for special party nights and fresh limes for Mexican-stye Margaritas.\r\n\r\nYou don''t want to miss this taste of Mexico in the cold of the Bradford winter', 'La Mexicanada', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '143-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 08:59:21', '2014-01-22 08:59:21', '', 143, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=508', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(509, 1, '2014-01-22 09:00:36', '2014-01-22 09:00:36', '[details address="100 Dissette St Bradford West Gwillimbury, ON L3Z 3G8" latitude="44.12058" longitude="-79.55852" phone="(905)775-9600" website="www.doncherryssportsgrill.com" hours="Sun to Thurs 11am - 11pm\r\n\r\nFri &amp; Sat 11am - 1am"]\r\n\r\nDon Cherry''s Sports Grill is the ultimate sports themed restaurant with great atmosphere, staff and food! Come check out the huge goalie mask, sports memorabilia and classic Don Cherry decor.\r\n\r\nThe menu offers many options for all age groups that includes classic favourites and those unique to our location. The menu is also sensitive to those with dietary needs by having options for those who may prefer gluten-free and vegetarian dishes. The establishment offers a large dining room, a sports bar for the sports enthusiast to catch the big game, the "Coaches Corner" party room for teams and groups of any kind and the "always sunny" patio.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Don Cherry’s', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '64-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 09:00:36', '2014-01-22 09:00:36', '', 64, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=509', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(510, 1, '2014-01-22 09:01:03', '2014-01-22 09:01:03', '[details address="305 Barrie St Bradford, ON L3Z 1M1" latitude="44.12611" longitude="-79.56768" phone="(905)775-9292" website="www.wimpysdiner.ca" hours="Mon to Thurs 8am - 9pm\r\n\r\nFri &amp; Sat 7am - 9pm\r\n\r\nSun 8am - 3pm"]\r\n\r\nWimpy’s Diner is a casual dining experience adorned with the 50’s and 60’s theme with coin operated juke boxes and decorated with memorabilia the atmosphere is unbelievable and so is the food. Wimpy’s of course is known for its Famous Hamburgers, morning and all day breakfast, specialty lunches and home style dinners.', 'Wimpy''s Diner', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '62-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 09:01:03', '2014-01-22 09:01:03', '', 62, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=510', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(511, 1, '2014-01-22 09:01:15', '2014-01-22 09:01:15', '[details address="300 Holland St W Bradford West Gwillimbury, ON L3Z 1H9" latitude="44.11177" longitude="-79.57599" phone="(905)775-0111" website="www.tinroofrestaurant.com" hours="Mon Closed\r\n\r\nTues to Sun 5pm - 10pm"]\r\n\r\nFeaturing the best in International cuisine. We would like to introduce our talented new Red Seal Chef Mike Fontaine french trained and creating some of the most delicious meals you''ll ever enjoy.\r\n\r\nBringing to Bradford some of the finest epicurean delights north of Toronto. Our new chef, Mike adds his own flavour into Italian favourites as well as international classics to our menu which features fresh seafood, steaks and locally grown produce.', 'Tin Roof', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '47-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 09:01:15', '2014-01-22 09:01:15', '', 47, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=511', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(512, 1, '2014-01-22 09:01:26', '2014-01-22 09:01:26', '[details address="17 Holland St. West, Bradford" latitude="44.11416" longitude="-79.56550" phone="(905)775-0599" website="" hours="Mon Closed\r\n\r\nTues to Sat 12pm - 11pm"]\r\n\r\nLusitano has room for up to 120 people in our elegant banquet room in downtown Bradford. Our menu includes fresh fish, seafood, steaks and BBQ chicken. And after a wonderful meal be sure to have our famous Cream of Heaven dessert. Our dining room is open for lunch and dinner every day except Monday. Reservations preferred.', 'Lusitano''s Restaurant', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 09:01:26', '2014-01-22 09:01:26', '', 1, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=512', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
