(562, 1, '2014-04-12 09:51:44', '2014-04-12 09:51:44', '<h3>ABOUT OUR CONTESTS</h3>\r\nGuests that buy any Bradfordlicious Special dinner or lunch and register your Bradfordlicious VIP Pass Rewards Card, can starting earning Vacation Points. The more times you and your family and buy a Bradfordlicious lunch or dinner, the more points you''ll earn giving you a greater chance to win our grand prize A Trip For Two Gift Voucher worth $1500 sponsored by Marlin Travel Bradford.\r\n<h3>HOW TO WIN</h3>\r\n1. Visit any participating Bradfordlicious Restaurant and buy any meal from their Bradfordlicious Menu\r\n2. Register your Bradfordlicious VIP Pass Rewards Card at any participating Bradfordlicious Restaurant and earn 1 Vacation Point per meal. 1 Vacation Point equals 1 contest entry.\r\n3. Visit a variety of Bradfordlicious Restaurants from more chances to win.\r\n4. Must follow us on Facebook or Twitter.\r\n5. Must be 19 or over to win and a legal Canadian resident.\r\n\r\nWinner will be selected on March 15th, 2014 and announced on Twitter &amp; Facebook.\r\n<h3>FOLLOW 2 WIN</h3>\r\nWe will be giving out free meals to our fans during the event so like our Facebook page or follow us on Twitter for your chance to win.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Bradfordlicious/633038696742636">www.facebooks.com/bradfordlicious\r\n</a><a href="https://twitter.com/Bradfordlicious">www.twitter.com/bradfordlicious</a>\r\n<h3>COMMENT 2 WIN</h3>\r\nVisit our website and tell us how your meal was at one of the restaurant pages. You could have the lucky review that wins a free meal.\r\n<a href="http://www.bradfordlicious.com" target="_blank">www.bradfordlicious.com</a>\r\n<h3>ABOUT THE BRADFORDLICIOUS VIP PASS REWARDS CARD</h3>\r\nThe Bradfordlicious VIP Pass Rewards Card is your GOLDEN PASS to be a part of an exclusive contest giving you a 1 in 1000 chance to win our grand trip prize. You can increase your odds of winning by visiting more Bradfordlicious Restaurants.\r\n\r\nThe Bradfordlicious VIP PASS Rewards Card is in association with Ricktag Rewards, a customer loyalty program that helps people save money in their community.', 'VIP Card', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '244-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-12 09:51:44', '2014-04-12 09:51:44', '', 244, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com/244-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
