(578, 1, '2014-04-13 17:23:00', '2014-04-13 17:23:00', 'Featuring the best in International cuisine. We would like to introduce our talented new Red Seal Chef Mike Fontaine french trained and creating some of the most delicious meals you''ll ever enjoy.\r\n\r\nBringing to Bradford some of the finest epicurean delights north of Toronto. Our new chef, Mike adds his own flavour into Italian favourites as well as international classics to our menu which features fresh seafood, steaks and locally grown produce.', 'Tin Roof', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '47-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-13 17:23:00', '2014-04-13 17:23:00', '', 47, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com/47-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
