(831, 1, '2015-01-24 18:56:44', '2015-01-24 18:56:44', '<h3>Title Sponsor <img class="alignright size-full wp-image-715" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Sponsor-Logo1.png" alt="Sponsor-Logo1" width="300" height="180" /></h3>\r\nBradfordlicious is very pleased to be working with Summerlyn Dental Care and have them as the Presenting Sponsor at the 2nd Annual Bradfordlicious. It did not take long for Dr. Zaid and his team to want to get involved and help support this new event. Summerlyn Dental Care’s commitment to giving back to the community sets the bar in town and their willingness to support these events shows loyalty and leadership in our community.\r\n\r\nAt Summerlyn – Summer Hill Dental Care, we believe that a dentist and patient become a team for treating an individual’s dental needs. Our physician spends most of his time listening to understand your concerns and responding with the best treatment options for you. With the help of our professional staff, he also follows up to make sure that general pain is relieved, problems are resolved and your health improves.\r\n\r\nTo connect with us, please visit our website at: <a href="http://www.smilesatsummerhilldental.com/bradford.html">http://www.summerlyndental.ca</a>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Sponsors', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '224-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-24 18:56:44', '2015-01-24 18:56:44', '', 224, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com/224-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
