(961, 1, '2015-02-05 06:12:52', '2015-02-05 06:12:52', 'Lusitano has room for up to 120 people in\r\nour elegant banquet room in downtown Bradford. Our menu includes fresh fish, seafood, steaks and BBQ chicken. And after a wonderful meal be sure to have our famous Cream of Heaven dessert. Our dining room is open for lunch and dinner every day except Monday. Reservations preferred.\r\n\r\n<strong>BRADFORDLICIOUS MENU</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Prix-fixe Dinner $20.15  |  Lunch $10.15</strong>\r\n\r\nDrinks, taxes &amp; gratuity extra.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Pick an Appetizer</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong><strong>Caesar Salad   |   Garden Salad  |  Grilled Squid w/house sauce</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong><strong>Lusitano’s Carrot Soup - </strong>Delicious home-made carrot soup made with Holland Marsh carrots and other local produce\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Pick a Lunch - served until 3pm</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Chicken Sandwich or Pork Sandwich served with fries</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong><strong>Grilled Chicken served with fries  </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong><strong>Pork Cutlet w/mushroom served with fries</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong><strong>Chicken Caesar Salad</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Pick an Entr</span></strong><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">ée - after 3pm</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Grilled Chicken Breast - </strong>Served with choice of potato, rice or vegetables\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong><strong>Grilled Squid - </strong>Served with choice of potato, rice or vegetables\r\n\r\n<strong>Pork &amp; Clams - </strong>Diced Pork Served with clams and diced potatoes\r\n\r\n<strong>Beef Cutlet - </strong>Served with fries and egg\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Pick a Dessert</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Natas Do Ceu (Heavenly Cream)   |   Homemade Pudding</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Chocolate Mouse   |   Ice Cream</strong>', 'Lusitano''s Restaurant', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-05 06:12:52', '2015-02-05 06:12:52', '', 1, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
